Package ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.database.tables

Class Table<T extends DocumentSerializable>

java.lang.Object
ca.cmput301t05.placeholder.database.tables.Table<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of document stored in the table, which should extend DocumentSerializable.
Direct Known Subclasses:
EventTable, ImageDetailTable, MilestoneTable, NotificationTable, ProfileTable
public abstract class Table<T extends DocumentSerializable> extends Object
The Table class is an abstract class that represents a table in the database. It provides methods for fetching and pushing documents to the table.
